---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Take-home Pay (IDR)
description: Calculate monthly take-home pay in Indonesia (PPh21, BPJS, JHT, pension).
permalink: /tools/salary/
---

<div class="w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col gap-12" x-data="salaryTool()" x-init="init()">
    {# Header #}
    {% set tool = {} %}
    {% for item in site.pages.tools.list %}
        {% if item.url == "/tools/salary/" %}
            {% set tool = item %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    {% set cat = site.pages.tools.categories[tool.tag] %}

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-center items-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border {{ cat.color }}">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">{{ cat.icon }}</span>
            {{ tool.tag }}
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl {{ cat.lightColor }} flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">{{ tool.icon }}</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-main font-display">
            {{ tool.title }}
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            {{ tool.description }}
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
            {% set shortcutHint = 'You can type shorthand values in salary fields: <span class="font-semibold text-text-main">250k</span>, <span class="font-semibold text-text-main">1.5m</span>, <span class="font-semibold text-text-main">1.2b</span>, or decimals like <span class="font-semibold text-text-main">1,5m</span> (case-insensitive).' %}
            {% include "partials/input-shortcut.njk" %}

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">person</span>
                    1. Income & Tax Profile
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-3xl space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                            <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">Monthly Basic Gross (IDR)</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="inputs.monthlyGross" @input="onCurrencyInput('monthlyGross')" @blur="onCurrencyBlur('monthlyGross')" placeholder="Enter amount (e.g. 10m)" class="block w-full px-5 py-4 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-main focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary text-lg transition-all" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                            <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">Other Allowances (optional)</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="inputs.monthlyAllowance" @input="onCurrencyInput('monthlyAllowance')" @blur="onCurrencyBlur('monthlyAllowance')" placeholder="Optional (e.g. 2m)" class="block w-full px-5 py-4 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-main focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary text-lg transition-all" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-2">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                            <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">Marital Status</label>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 p-1 bg-white" role="tablist">
                                    <button :class="status.married ? 'text-text-muted hover:bg-stone-50' : 'bg-stone-900 border-transparent text-white shadow-sm'" @click="status.married=false; recalculate()" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all">Single (TK)</button>
                                    <button :class="status.married ? 'bg-stone-900 border-transparent text-white shadow-sm' : 'text-text-muted hover:bg-stone-50'" @click="status.married=true; recalculate()" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all">Married (K)</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:items-start items-stretch">
                            <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">Dependents (max 3)</label>
                            <input type="number" min="0" max="3" x-model.number="status.dependents" @input="recalculate()" class="block w-full md:w-32 px-5 py-3.5 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-main focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary transition-all text-center" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-blue-50/50 border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-row items-center justify-between mt-2">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500">policy</span>
                            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-800">TER Tax Category (PMK 168/2023)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600/70" x-text="getPTKPCode()"></span>
                            <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm" x-text="'Category ' + getTERCategory()"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">receipt_long</span>
                    2. Employee Deductions (Potongan)
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-3xl space-y-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">BPJS Kesehatan %</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.bpjs" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">Perpres 64/2020</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">JHT (Hari Tua) %</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.jht" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">PP 46/2015</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">JP (Pensiun) %</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.pension" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">PP 45/2015</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="pt-5 border-t border-stone-200 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">BPJS Kes Wage Cap (IDR)</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="capInputs.bpjs" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">Max base for calc (Perpres 64/2020)</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">JP/Pension Wage Cap (IDR)</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="capInputs.pension" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">Max base for calc (updated yearly)</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">corporate_fare</span>
                    3. Employer Contributions (Tunjangan)
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-3xl space-y-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">BPJS Kesehatan %</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.bpjsEmployer" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">Perpres 64/2020</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">JHT (Hari Tua) %</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.jhtEmployer" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">PP 46/2015</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">JP (Pensiun) %</label>
                            <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.pensionEmployer" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center" />
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">PP 45/2015</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="pt-5 border-t border-stone-200">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                                <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">Company Industry Risk (JKK)</label>
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <select x-model="jkkTier" @change="recalculate()" class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-main appearance-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary transition-all text-sm">
                                        <template x-for="tier in jkkTiers" :key="tier.tier">
                                            <option :value="tier.tier" x-text="tier.name"></option>
                                        </template>
                                    </select>
                                    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center px-4 text-stone-400">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">expand_more</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                                <label class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted ml-1">JKM (Kematian) %</label>
                                <input type="text" x-model="rateInputs.jkm" disabled class="block w-full px-4 py-3 bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl text-text-muted cursor-not-allowed text-center md:text-left" />
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-text-muted ml-1 mt-0.5">Fixed at 0.30% (PP 44/2015)</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50/50 border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-row items-center justify-between mt-4">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500">health_and_safety</span>
                                <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-800">JKK Tier Rules (PP 44/2015)</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600/70" x-text="m.jkkTierData?.label"></span>
                                <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm" x-text="m.jkkTierData?.rate + '%'"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-end pt-2">
                <button @click="reset()" class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-stone-100 hover:bg-stone-200 text-sm font-bold text-text-muted transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">refresh</span>
                    Reset Values
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 text-text-main p-6 md:p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-blue-500"></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:gap-12 relative z-10">
                    
                    <!-- Left: Payslip -->
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">receipt</span>
                            Monthly Payslip Simulation
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="font-mono text-[14px]">
                            <!-- Basic Income -->
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1.5">
                                <span class="text-stone-500">Gross Income (Basic + Allowance)</span><span class="font-semibold text-right text-stone-900" x-text="format(m.monthlyGross)"></span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- The 'Hidden' Additions -->
                            <div class="mt-3 bg-white rounded-xl p-3 border border-stone-200">
                                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-stone-400 mb-2">Plus: Mandatory Benefit Additions (TER Base)</div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-500">
                                    <span>BPJS Kes (Employer)</span><span class="text-right" x-text="format(m.monthlyBPJSEmployer)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-500">
                                    <span>BPJS JKK (Employer: <span x-text="m.jkkTierData?.rate + '%'"></span>)</span><span class="text-right" x-text="format(m.jkkMonthly)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-500">
                                    <span>BPJS JKM (Employer: 0.30%)</span><span class="text-right" x-text="format(m.jkmMonthly)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 pt-2 mt-2 border-t border-stone-200 font-bold text-stone-800">
                                    <span>Taxable TER Base</span><span class="text-right" x-text="format(m.taxableGross)"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Deductions -->
                            <div class="mt-4">
                                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted mb-2 mt-4 border-b border-stone-200 pb-2">Minus: Employee Deductions</div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-600">
                                    <span>PPh21 Tax</span><span class="text-right text-red-500" x-text="'-' + format(m.monthlyTax)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-600">
                                    <span>BPJS Kes</span><span class="text-right text-red-500" x-text="'-' + format(m.monthlyBPJS)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-600">
                                    <span>BPJS JHT</span><span class="text-right text-red-500" x-text="'-' + format(m.monthlyJHT)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1 text-stone-600">
                                    <span>BPJS JP (Pension)</span><span class="text-right text-red-500" x-text="'-' + format(m.monthlyPension)"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Take Home -->
                            <div class="mt-5 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-5">
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 mb-3 pb-3 border-b border-primary/20">
                                    <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary pr-2">PTKP Status (<span x-text="getPTKPCode()"></span>)</span>
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-right tabular-nums text-primary" x-text="format(m.ptkpValue)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 mb-4 pb-3 border-b border-primary/20">
                                    <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary">TER Tax Category <span x-text="m.terCategory"></span></span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white bg-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs" x-text="m.terRate + '% rate'"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4">
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Take-Home Pay</span>
                                    <span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary" x-text="format(m.takeHome)"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Right: Annual Summary -->
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">inventory</span>
                            Dec. Annual Reconciliation
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="font-mono text-[14px]">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1.5 border-b border-stone-100">
                                <span class="text-stone-500 pr-2">Gross Setup (Inc. Tunjangan)</span>
                                <span class="font-semibold text-right tabular-nums text-stone-900" x-text="format(m.annualGrossIncome)"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1.5 border-b border-stone-100">
                                <span class="text-stone-500 pr-2">Biaya Jabatan (5% max)</span>
                                <span class="font-semibold text-right text-red-500 tabular-nums whitespace-nowrap" x-text="'-' + format(m.annualBiayaJabatan)"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1.5 border-b border-stone-100">
                                <span class="text-stone-500 pr-2">Tunjangan Pensiun/JHT</span><span class="font-semibold text-right text-red-500 tabular-nums whitespace-nowrap" x-text="'-' + format(m.annualContributions)"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 py-1.5 border-b border-stone-100">
                                <span class="text-stone-500 pr-2">Tax-Free Income (PTKP)</span>
                                <span class="font-semibold text-right tabular-nums text-stone-900" x-text="'-' + format(m.ptkpValue)"></span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mt-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-stone-200">
                                <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted mb-3">Tarif Pasal 17 Progressif</div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 mb-2 pb-2 border-b border-stone-100">
                                    <span class="text-stone-600 font-semibold text-xs">A. Total 1-Year True Tax</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-stone-900 tabular-nums whitespace-nowrap" x-text="format(m.exactAnnualTax)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4 mb-3 pb-3 border-b border-stone-100">
                                    <span class="text-stone-500 text-xs">B. Withheld Jan-Nov (TER)</span>
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-stone-700 tabular-nums whitespace-nowrap" x-text="'-' + format(m.taxPaidJanNov)"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-x-4">
                                    <span class="font-bold text-stone-900 text-sm">Dec Final Tax (A - B)</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold tabular-nums whitespace-nowrap px-2 py-1 rounded" :class="m.decemberTax < 0 ? 'text-green-600 bg-green-50' : 'text-red-500 bg-red-50'" x-text="format(m.decemberTax)"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-[10px] leading-5 text-stone-500">TER monthly deductions are an estimate. Exact liability calculated at year end using standard Pasal 17 rates. December tax reconciles any difference.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-stone-200">
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-800 mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">policy</span>
                        Regulations & Rules
                    </h3>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">receipt_long</span></div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-800 text-sm">TER Tax Method (PMK 168/2023)</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">Berlaku Jan 2024. PPh 21 bulanan dihitung: <strong>Penghasilan Bruto × Tarif Kategori (A/B/C)</strong>. Desember menggunakan tarif progresif tahunan (Pasal 17).</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">group</span></div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-800 text-sm">PTKP (PMK 101/2016)</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">Batas penghasilan bebas pajak. <strong>TK/0:</strong> Rp54 juta/thn. Tanggungan/Kawin masing-masing menambah Rp4,5 juta/thn (maks 3 tanggungan).</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">health_and_safety</span></div>
